data.description: Enjoy the serenity of the lake in this gated community while relaxing in the open concept living room or on the lanai of in this gorgeous 2-bedroom 2.5 bath townhouse. This end unit townhome features a large loft that can easily be converted to a 3rd bedroom. The kitchen has stainless steel appliances and granite countertops. Additional entertaining space is provided by the paved patio.  Community amenities include, biking and jogging path, Racquetball, pool, spa, fitness center, game room and clubhouse.
